com.cognifide.slice.core.internal.injector

Interface InjectorLifecycleListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdapterFactoryManager

    @ConsumerType
public interface InjectorLifecycleListener
    OSGi services implementing this interface will be informed about events related to the Slice injector lifecycle. It gets more information about the created/destroyed injector than InjectorListener and is meant to be used internally.
    Author:
    Tomasz RÄ™kawek
